{"tid":1379962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣組留意】政府開始打經濟民生牌，恐嚇市民經濟會雙位數負增長","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:15:53.000Z","uid":36324,"like":301,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"03a86470b730cdf17d9c75706d1c9580d370c48b","tid":1379962,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"星期六星期日周末接連兩日，都有高層官員開口話示威影響市道同信心，最終影響就業<br />\n<br />\n1. 邱騰華接受訪問，恐嚇聲稱年尾經濟指標可能出現雙位數負增長；又話因為示威場面激烈，所以多少對香港有負面影響<br />\n<br />\n2. 陳茂波在網誌聲稱 //外圍不明朗持續困擾本港經濟，近期的社會事件令本地市況更為疲弱，香港短期經濟展望難言樂觀// ，又話 //抗議行動持續時間愈長，對中小企、小商戶的影響將更為顯著，部份市民的生計亦會受到拖累。//<br />\n<br />\n似乎係政府將會舊調重彈，再打返經濟牌一招<br />\n<br />\n<strong>呢一刻呢鼓風向仲未吹得起，可以唔洗咁快回應 (否則變相幫手起風)，但一定要留意住，準備隨時反擊</strong><br />\n<br />\n當然大部分抗爭者可能樂見經濟轉差，但對公眾既文宣問題仍然需要處理<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得可以講：<br />\n<br />\n(a) 本身外圍經濟差，香港咁國際化既經濟體一定跟住差<br />\n(b) 以香港既經濟規模，出現雙位數負增長係好誇張 (2018 GDP 計，可以等於成個愛沙尼亞 / 拉脫維亞既全年 GDP)<br />\n(c) 而家香港既經濟結構，就算經濟好都唔會惠及到一般人<br />\n(d) 香港經濟結構傾斜既核心原因之一，就係呢個人民無法更換，人民代表無法監督既非民選獨裁殖民政權<br />\n(e) 同樣因為呢個獨裁殖民政權並非向香港人問責，類似逃犯條例、直接威脅香港經濟生死存亡既野只會陸續有來<br />\n(f) 如果經濟係咁差，特首咁多日都唔出黎，係完全不負責任<br />\n(g) 最後，香港人有無呢份堅持，假如真係要犧牲經濟，都要爭取自由同正義？係咪因為經濟會差，所以黑警就可以亂打人唔洗負責？養大黑警、包庇黑警同一切壓逼既始作俑者中共/港共政權，係咪可以繼續獨裁落去？"},{"pid":"ebd7e3261fe5103cc3c9b0969da14d47b216172b","tid":1379962,"uid":44358,"like":298,"dislike":0,"score":298,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"真係好笑，負增長就賴市民，加速增長就話 Chi Na 帶動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499ba6fe95f387ee7b7e9037905b0d14227f7762","tid":1379962,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"58e248b1c361dfe0cf9234af9b7803c8bb956f4d","tid":1379962,"uid":4574,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"經濟差=政府管治無能"},{"pid":"add8997a957986186d7ab23c5575b1fb9ed7d387","tid":1379962,"uid":253016,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"事實係<br />\n經濟好=支那可以瘋狂吸血<br />\n經濟唔好=還富於民"},{"pid":"23b104a7113cba61ce9524091b126cf44518f4e7","tid":1379962,"uid":155902,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:01:35.000Z","msg":"近呢幾年政府啲垃圾工程敗家數字都夠多la 掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙中線, 西九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882eb918cf3c50e2b181387a8fb655893554b014","tid":1379962,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb5fc221773437f02822c0d6fe0e3d7158da8955","tid":1379962,"uid":12412,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"啲錢一早倒哂落海啦"},{"pid":"0366d0b9691c46fdc52c90673584d8795aadec95","tid":1379962,"uid":90601,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:04:35.000Z","msg":"政府一早回應訴求咪唔會有示威"},{"pid":"210d9fd9aaa1a2f43151440f1eeaede4156d7f62","tid":1379962,"uid":161098,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"經濟差？<br />\n$10叉飯同雲吞麵出返黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大快活早排仲加咗價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8c8996e9fe806ce6cae66ac3ad47bb7c4e17be","tid":1379962,"uid":62749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"佢地最鍾意倒果為因"},{"pid":"62224fb7366c7e1811ed56f356b597afd4f8ffee","tid":1379962,"uid":83251,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:13:32.000Z","msg":"就係你地管得廢才負增長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a043ed7ab6d8fccc9fa31ced8c01fb6217e9ab28","tid":1379962,"uid":258696,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"義士= 5000億美金守護者<br />\n反送中 保5000億"},{"pid":"3142e6a1799cfc6689096a68500a62b282d115be","tid":1379962,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樂見其成</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7e886c71969d2d6ea598f9200f6b34ea834bdd1b","tid":1379962,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"仲有樣, 聯繫匯率唔係用黎穩定經濟<br />\n而係令市民百上加斤<br />\n因為經濟一仆, 冇左自我調節功能<br />\n呢樣仲成為中港資本家剝削港人財技"},{"pid":"7d43ab50d72479fdc2c4618e9df874d6254cce8e","tid":1379962,"uid":77196,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"老老實實，經濟就算雙位數增長，普通市民都唔會點樣享受到，都係高位離地果班食撚哂，既然係咁不如攬炒洗牌啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8f3468fce2079c21ff3029fb10a571bf54fe7e","tid":1379962,"uid":285523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:20:23.000Z","msg":"互推<br />\n【警告】唔好令今次運動瓦解於自己手中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378948</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要Fact Check<br />\n要用Telegram<br />\n<blockquote>Telegram channel 整合<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205184\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205184</a></blockquote><br />\n要包容及理性討論<br />\n唔好一味煽動情緒<br />\n切勿濫用加密</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f7d2c2fc71115841b512b7bef43e206bff72304","tid":1379962,"uid":49144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d43ab50d72479fdc2c4618e9df874d6254cce8e","tid":1379962,"uid":77196,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"老老實實，經濟就算雙位數增長，普通市民都唔會點樣享受到，都係高位離地果班食撚哂，既然係咁不如攬炒洗牌啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"6f83efa22d82aa96a805da8d6365669d26cc1068","tid":1379962,"uid":26389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"on79 反送中背後有歐洲議會+美國國會加持<br />\n評級機構都出埋聲話示威有助提高香港主權評級<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20190706-權威評級機構穆迪預測香港一國兩制撐不到50年\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20190706-%E6%AC%8A%E5%A8%81%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%A9%86%E8%BF%AA%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E6%92%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B050%E5%B9%B4&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=40efab27\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/中國/20190706-權威評級機構穆迪預測香港一國兩制撐不到50年</a><br />\n唔支持示威先危害經濟<br />\n邊個地區既經濟唔是靠歐美"},{"pid":"a231c88f3dfe14f836c2ea574268b9be821f29c6","tid":1379962,"uid":25183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"負增長啫，又唔係要蝕"},{"pid":"46ae4f9742e9ae756a0bda8848cacedd0f600bca","tid":1379962,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:24:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffe560a794ae3b97cbebb1052c8551c0fa52f132","tid":1379962,"uid":188176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:25:45.000Z","msg":"個指標食得ga咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸夠年年增長<br />\nd廠咪又係係咁執"},{"pid":"b691f7e2d753ac906b53fa9ca6f11842c1b146fe","tid":1379962,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e248b1c361dfe0cf9234af9b7803c8bb956f4d","tid":1379962,"uid":4574,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"經濟差=政府管治無能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"大大力bam落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e201bede618c69f71dd5635592b27d114927944","tid":1379962,"uid":125590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"780bd995955131e23ac234e6a0548fb7cb870e50","tid":1379962,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd7e